## How These Rules Work

- **alwaysApply: true** - Rules that are always included in every chat session (critical rules)
- **globs: ["pattern"]** - Rules that apply when working with specific file patterns
- **description only** - Rules that are intelligently applied when the Agent determines they're relevant

## Critical Warnings

⚠️ **DO NOT manually edit files in `docs/roles/`** - These are auto-generated by `scripts/generate_pages.py`

⚠️ **Always use the virtual environment** - Never install packages globally. Use `venv/bin/python3` or activate venv first.

⚠️ **Regenerate pages after script changes** - After modifying `scripts/generate_pages.py`, always regenerate all role pages.

